Kairo Kingdom have had an amazing debut year: discovered by Simplify, their debut EP "One Two/ Boombox" hit #1 on the glitch-hop charts and firmly planted the duo in the crates of DJ elite worldwide. Soon, they were picked up by the mighty Mau5trap for "The Sound of Now" and did some killer electro for Big Fish. To round the year out right, these pioneers of weird, bangin dance grooves bring their impeccable vibe to Play Me for a 4 track EP of heavy goodness. Prepare for impact!
